{"tid":1769493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《願榮光》令商台陷兩難","createTime":"2019-12-05T02:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T14:16:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9df72715460ded02bc0011bcf62abcf22570d582","tid":1769493,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191205/20819126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F20819126&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=1faa4ed2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191205%2F20819126&h=6d46df4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191205/20819126</a><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光》令商台陷兩難<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191205/large/1575464698_7cdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191205%2Flarge%2F1575464698_7cdf.jpg&h=106b0b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《願榮光歸香港》是否有機會搶入《叱咤》「我最喜愛的歌曲」，後日是死線。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n商台昨日宣佈取消明年舉行《叱咤樂壇頒獎禮》，相信是要避免陷入兩難局面，因為網民最關注的《願榮光歸香港》，有機會因投票成為年度「我最喜愛的歌曲」，而一旦《願榮光歸香港》獲獎，更在台上領獎及表演，商台定必會受到內地及港府壓力，分分鐘背上宣揚及支持「港獨」黑鑊，雖然商台的牌照至2028年才屆滿，但續牌問題長遠上仍要面對。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：《勁歌》隨時變錄影<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191205/large/1575464697_3fde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191205%2Flarge%2F1575464697_3fde.jpg&h=ef64611b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《撐起雨傘》以總票數2,887票當選「我最喜愛的歌曲」，當日台下有不少觀眾舉黃傘、氣球撐場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191205/large/1575464697_5e40.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191205%2Flarge%2F1575464697_5e40.gif&h=eaa02dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反，如果歌曲未能得獎，現場也怕會有難以預料的事發生，對出席的歌手難免造成壓力，所以最好方法是不搞現場頒獎禮，避過所有尷尬或示威場面。早前《願榮光歸香港》排除萬難派台，截至昨日已在商台網頁上獲13萬個like，但要上榜，還得要靠DJ於節目中播歌，後日是入圍「死線」，商台在「死線」前取消頒獎禮，也避免歌曲若成功上榜才宣佈取消頒獎禮會引起的各種揣測。<br />\n<br />\n2014年雨傘運動，代表真普選的歌曲《撐起雨傘》便於2015年元旦舉行的《叱咤》頒獎禮上奪得「我最喜愛的歌曲」，當晚黃耀明、素顏黑衣的何韻詩及葉德嫻掛黃絲帶上台，聯同方皓玟、RubberBand等演繹歌曲，台下有觀眾舉黃傘、氣球在場內遊走，甚至有觀眾激動到喊。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：翁可人 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n《勁歌》隨時變錄影<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【男女五強】周國賢強鬥姜濤<br />\n<br />\n《勁歌》隨時變錄影<br />\n【男女五強】周國賢強鬥姜濤<br />\n稱未能確保參與者安全 保留網上投票商台取消《叱咤》頒獎禮"},{"pid":"f780fc8c9aa47be41921f2616f880b4d77f1e06b","tid":1769493,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:41:13.000Z","msg":"英國美國加拿大都攻擊緊中國<br />\n但啲tweets無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Rt + like + reply</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=d346188b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task2</span></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"7607ad5b10dbdc498b93562e0f9ef7098f93bdc6","tid":1769493,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"《叱咤樂壇頒獎禮》商台唔攪，網民攪<br />\n1月1日晚 維園見<br />\n發夢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}